<text top="1081" left="822" width="10" height="14" font="13"><b>3 </b></text>
<text top="1081" left="90" width="44" height="12" font="14">06-45429 </text>
<text top="1096" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="13"><b> </b></text>
<text top="132" left="126" width="330" height="17" font="3">start of democratic rule. The people who will be </text>
<text top="150" left="126" width="337" height="17" font="3">destined to lead the country will bear the </text>
<text top="168" left="126" width="336" height="17" font="3">important responsibility to provide long-term </text>
<text top="186" left="126" width="335" height="17" font="3">foundations for the restoration of peace and </text>
<text top="204" left="126" width="345" height="17" font="3">stability, national reconciliation and the </text>
